data.title: Products Dell Technologies and EMC
data.meta_description: HDF authorized distributor of Dell: Laptops and desktop computers (Inspiron, Latitude, XPS, Alienware...), servers, monitors and projectors, accessories.
data.text:
Dell Technologies Authorized Distributor

Dell and EMC joined forces in the largest technology merger in history to become Dell Technologies. Dell Technologies unites seven technology leaders – Dell, Dell EMC, Pivotal, RSA, Secureworks, Virtustream and VMware – in one company with the power to drive digital transformation and generate real results every day for the customers and for people who partner with us.
